587
00:40:04,026 --> 00:40:05,861
-Oh, look, Na-bi made it after all.
-Give me that.

588
00:40:05,945 --> 00:40:07,696
-Hi, Na-bi.
-So, where can I sit?

589
00:40:07,780 --> 00:40:09,198
