He's not like that at all.

606
00:40:49,738 --> 00:40:51,073
Where will he sit when he gets here?

607
00:40:51,157 --> 00:40:52,575
We can put another chair here.

608
00:40:52,658 --> 00:40:54,243
"Jae-eon's not the type
to date," huh?

609
00:40:54,326 --> 00:40:56,996
Seems to me
he's dating all the girls in school.

610
00:40:57,079 --> 00:40:58,497
Park Jae-eon's really popular.

611
00:41:02,668 --> 00:41:06,505
