613
00:41:07,882 --> 00:41:10,342
No way. Are you sure Sol's coming?

614
00:41:10,426 --> 00:41:13,345
Ji-wan's coming too, in case you didn't
hear her name. It's not just Sol.

615
00:41:13,429 --> 00:41:15,181
Great, great, great!
A chair, a chair, a chair.

616
00:41:15,264 --> 00:41:16,724
Oh, wow.

617
00:41:16,807 --> 00:41:18,309
Nice to know you haven't changed a bit.

618
00:41:18,392 --> 00:41:19,810
-Why is it next to you?
-Shut up.

619
00:41:22,605 --> 00:41:23,439
Wanna take it off?

620
00:41:25,566 --> 00:41:26,442
