623
00:41:34,033 --> 00:41:35,451
Take your jacket off, too.

624
00:41:36,744 --> 00:41:38,537
I wasn't thinking of anything.

625
00:41:38,621 --> 00:41:40,998
It's so hot.
Just take your jackets off.

626
00:41:41,081 --> 00:41:43,083
-You take yours off.
-Oh, that water's mine.

627
00:41:44,543 --> 00:41:46,962
Oh, uh, I'm sorry.
Is there another cup I can use?

628
00:41:47,046 --> 00:41:48,422
No, it's fine.

629
00:41:49,715 --> 00:41:52,218
Oh, you're my senior, right?

630
00:41:52,968 --> 00:41:55,638
Nice to meet you, Na-bi.
I'm Kim Eun-han, a freshman.

631
00:41:57,806 --> 00:42:00,726
