as I started to get bored…

643
00:42:21,789 --> 00:42:23,165
-Has he replied?
-No.

644
00:42:23,249 --> 00:42:25,751
-…the star of the show showed up.
-Oh, Jae-eon's here.

645
00:42:25,834 --> 00:42:27,378
-Hey!
-What took you so long?

646
00:42:27,461 --> 00:42:29,171
-Hi!
-Jae-eon!

647
00:42:29,255 --> 00:42:31,674
-Why are you only getting here now?
-You're so late.

648
00:42:31,757 --> 00:42:33,384
Here, Jae-eon!

649
00:42:33,467 --> 00:42:36,804
The room gets filled with
sexual tension whenever Jae-eon is there.

650
00:42:36,887 --> 00:42:38,973
-You better make up for being late!
-Dude, what took you so long?

651
00:42:39,056 --> 00:42:40,599
The traffic was so bad, I'm sorry.

652
00:42:41,934 --> 00:42:44,645
Hey, Na-bi… it's good to see you here.

653
00:42:45,229 --> 00:42:46,272
Oh, thanks.

654
00:42:47,022 --> 00:42:49,108
Jae-eon's finally here,
let's drink!

655
00:42:49,191 --> 00:42:50,484
-Yeah, yeah, yeah!
-All right!

656
00:42:50,568 --> 00:42:52,027
Cheers!

657
00:42:52,111 --> 00:42:54,280
-Cheers, everyone.
-Cheers.

658
00:42:54,363 --> 00:42:56,782
-There you go. Cheers!
-Drink up, guys.

659
00:42:58,534 --> 00:43:00,953
