686
00:44:00,054 --> 00:44:02,723
Eating something spicy
is about feeling a sense of pain.

687
00:44:02,806 --> 00:44:05,267
Stop treating me like a pervert.

688
00:44:05,768 --> 00:44:07,728
Hey, Min-sang,
use this to wipe your mouth.

689
00:44:08,729 --> 00:44:11,315
Oh, awesome. That was smart. Great, great.

690
00:44:11,398 --> 00:44:12,941
-Stop it, Se-hun.
-Shh.

691
00:44:21,367 --> 00:44:23,285
Hey!

692
00:44:24,787 --> 00:44:26,789
Min-sang, have a drink.

693
00:44:27,665 --> 00:44:28,832
-I'll move here.
-Oh, come on!

694
00:44:28,916 --> 00:44:30,292
-I've done nothing wrong!
-Because you should!

695
00:44:30,376 --> 00:44:31,418
Are you getting a drink?

696
00:44:32,544 --> 00:44:34,004
