721
00:45:54,585 --> 00:45:57,421
You weren't like that before.
You used to smile all the time.

722
00:45:58,213 --> 00:45:59,631
I thought you were so angry.

723
00:45:59,715 --> 00:46:01,175
Gosh, Min-sang.
What's wrong with you?

724
00:46:01,258 --> 00:46:03,302
Why do you keep bugging Na-bi today?

725
00:46:04,928 --> 00:46:05,888
Hey.

726
00:46:06,930 --> 00:46:08,599
Are you guys seeing each other?

727
00:46:09,391 --> 00:46:11,018
You act strange when you're together.

728
00:46:11,602 --> 00:46:13,687
I knew there was something going on.

729
00:46:13,771 --> 00:46:14,772
Well, it's really--

730
00:46:14,855 --> 00:46:16,231
No, you got it all wrong.

731
00:46:17,191 --> 00:46:19,151
Oh, come on, don't lie to me.

732
00:46:19,234 --> 00:46:21,028
It's so obvious,
the way you two look at each other.

733
00:46:21,111 --> 00:46:22,321
What's up with you?

734
00:46:22,404 --> 00:46:23,906
