735
00:46:25,115 --> 00:46:26,241
Right, Na-bi?

736
00:46:30,829 --> 00:46:32,331
Yeah.

737
00:46:32,414 --> 00:46:33,332
That's right.

738
00:46:33,415 --> 00:46:35,334
Nothing, you say?

739
00:46:35,417 --> 00:46:36,794
