746
00:46:51,725 --> 00:46:54,269
so he said that because
he doesn't want things to get awkward.

747
00:46:54,978 --> 00:46:56,104
Just forget it.

748
00:46:56,188 --> 00:46:59,775
Because if that were really the case,
then he would've just changed the subject

749
00:46:59,858 --> 00:47:02,194
or would've given
a vague answer or something.

750
00:47:05,489 --> 00:47:06,365
Right, Na-bi?

751
00:47:06,448 --> 00:47:09,993
Jae-eon didn't just say that
for the sake of giving an answer.

752
00:47:11,161 --> 00:47:12,079
He just drew the line.

753
00:47:12,162 --> 00:47:14,248
Hey, don't be like that.

754
00:47:14,832 --> 00:47:16,375
Na-bi, you're overreacting.

755
00:47:16,458 --> 00:47:17,835
You know something like this could happen.

756
00:47:17,918 --> 00:47:19,044
Why are you encouraging me?

757
00:47:19,127 --> 00:47:22,089
Well… I just thought maybe
I was too harsh before.

758
00:47:22,172 --> 00:47:24,591
It's not like
I have the power to read minds.

759
00:47:24,675 --> 00:47:27,135
And also, I noticed
he couldn't stop looking at you.

760
00:47:29,137 --> 00:47:31,390
So not true.
He was busy talking to Yun-ji.

761
00:47:31,473 --> 00:47:35,185
I swear! He kept staring at you
whenever you had something to say.

762
00:47:35,686 --> 00:47:37,354
And most importantly,

763
00:47:40,607 --> 00:47:42,568
Jae-eon never does stuff like this.

764
00:47:46,905 --> 00:47:49,408
Bit-na, it's just a canned drink.

765
00:47:50,200 --> 00:47:52,202
Oh, this is so much better.

766
00:47:52,703 --> 00:47:56,081
To be honest, I wasn't sure
when I only heard your side of the story,

767
00:47:56,164 --> 00:47:58,876
but when I saw you in one room,
I felt something.

768
00:48:04,464 --> 00:48:05,924
What do you wanna do now?

769
00:48:06,008 --> 00:48:07,634
Well, what I want is to go home.

770
00:48:08,635 --> 00:48:10,387
Let's invite Jae-eon to your place.
What do you think?

771
00:48:10,470 --> 00:48:12,848
What's wrong with you?
I don't wanna do that, Bit-na.

772
00:48:12,931 --> 00:48:14,349
Come on, I'll go with you!

773
00:48:14,433 --> 00:48:16,351
You can't waste
such a beautiful opportunity.

774
00:48:17,769 --> 00:48:18,604
But still…

775
00:48:20,647 --> 00:48:23,400
Never mind, I'll just go home.

776
00:48:23,483 --> 00:48:24,651
