777
00:48:25,694 --> 00:48:27,195
Well, let's at least give it a shot.

778
00:48:27,279 --> 00:48:28,363
Bit-na.

779
00:48:28,947 --> 00:48:31,241
You swear there's really nothing going on?

780
00:48:31,825 --> 00:48:33,911
